"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        Past history of severe vasovagal reactivity",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td class=\"subtitle1_single\">",
"        For the Cu T 380A IUD only",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
